Classification of the state of tomato for consumption

This is a Tomatoe state Classiffication with Python 2.7 Programming Language, with OpenCV 2.4

For Classification of the state of tomato for consumption (by color), 
use 3D RGB histogram for image descriptor, This histogram will be used to characterize the color of the tomatoe, which is a good starting
point for classifying the state of a tomatoe. Masking is used to focus on the AOI (Area of Interest), RandomForestClassifier is used for classification.

